=== 拍攝和後期製作 ===
[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]於2019年10月21日在[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[克利夫兰|克利夫兰]]進行<ref name="Cleveland19">{{cite web|url=https://www.cleveland19.com/2019/09/30/get-out-actors-film-black-panther-biopic-cleveland-movie-extras-needed/|title='Get Out' actors to film Black Panther Party biopic in Cleveland, movie extras needed|website=Cleveland19.com|first=Misty|last=Stiver|date=2019-09-30|access-date=2019-10-20|archive-date=2019-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020173618/https://www.cleveland19.com/2019/09/30/get-out-actors-film-black-panther-biopic-cleveland-movie-extras-needed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年11月25日至26日，劇組在[[曼斯菲尔德_(俄亥俄州)|曼斯菲尔德]]的[[俄亥俄州立感化院|俄亥俄州立感化院]]取景<ref name="MNJ">{{cite web|url=https://www.mansfieldnewsjournal.com/story/news/2019/11/26/naacp-fred-hampton-movie-filming-mansfield/4295500002/|title=Movie on NAACP martyr Fred Hampton filming in Mansfield|last=Tuggle|first=Zach|work=Mansfield News Journal|publisher=[[Gannett|Gannett]]|date=2019-11-26|access-date=2020-07-31|archive-date=2019-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128090047/https://www.mansfieldnewsjournal.com/story/news/2019/11/26/naacp-fred-hampton-movie-filming-mansfield/4295500002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歷時42天，製作於2019年12月19日結束<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B6R9p9clDOT/|title=42 days and it's a wrap! After 3 months in production, 2 years in development and just over 50 years after the assassination of Chairman Fred Hampton, my heart is full of gratitude, respect and love. It was a needle-moving, eye-opening and completely step-outside-of-the-comfort-zone experience. To this incredible team of artists, filmmakers, partners and crewmembers, it was an honor to work alongside you to tell the important story of this extraordinary man. Stay tuned.|via=[[Instagram|Instagram]]|first=Charles|last=D. King|date=2019-12-19|access-date=2019-12-28}}</ref>。片名原為《耶穌是我同夥》（{{lang|en|''Jesus Was My Homeboy''}}）<ref name="DH1">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/ryan-coogler-black-panthers-warner-bros-daniel-kaluuya-lakeith-stanfield-macro-fred-hampton-1202559976/|title=Ryan Coogler & MACRO Set Black Panthers Pic With Warner Bros; Daniel Kaluuya & Lakeith Stanfield In Talks To Star|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Andreas|last=Wiseman|date=2019-02-19|access-date=2019-10-20|archive-date=2019-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020173616/https://deadline.com/2019/02/ryan-coogler-black-panthers-warner-bros-daniel-kaluuya-lakeith-stanfield-macro-fred-hampton-1202559976/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，經歷一段名稱未定的時間前<ref name="THR1"/><ref name="MNJ"/>，電影暫稱為《猶大與黑色彌賽亞》（{{lang|en|''Judas and the Black Messiah''}}）<ref name="Cleveland19"/>。剪輯師克里斯汀·斯普拉格（{{lang|en|Kristan Sprague}}）於2020年1月開始剪輯該片，此前數十家工作室因[[2019冠状病毒病纽约州疫情|紐約COVID-19疫情]]而被關閉，後來導致工作人員在後期製作期間以視訊交流方式進行遠程工作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/judas-and-the-black-messiah-shaka-king-sean-bobbitt-podcast-interview-sundance-film-festival-1234684992/|title='Judas And The Black Messiah': Director Shaka King & DP Sean Bobbitt On Finding Late 1960s Chicago In Cleveland – Sundance Crew Call Podcast|date=2021-02-01|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201231346/https://deadline.com/2021/02/judas-and-the-black-messiah-shaka-king-sean-bobbitt-podcast-interview-sundance-film-festival-1234684992/|archive-date=2021-02-01|access-date=2021-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年7月，《猶大與黑色彌賽亞》確認為正式片名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://relevantmagazine.com/culture/ryan-cooglers-fred-hampton-biopic-has-a-new-name-judas-and-the-black-messiah/|title=Ryan Coogler's Fred Hampton Biopic Has a New Name: 'Judas and the Black Messiah'|website=Relevant|date=2020-07-30|access-date=2020-07-31|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801053301/https://relevantmagazine.com/culture/ryan-cooglers-fred-hampton-biopic-has-a-new-name-judas-and-the-black-messiah/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 音樂 ==
