== 發行 ==
《猶大與黑色彌賽亞》於{{le|2021年日舞影展|2021 Sundance Film Festival|2021年2月1日}}在[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]上全球首映，包括虛擬放映和現場放映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/judas-and-the-black-messiah-sundance-film-festival-1234883365/|title=Judas and the Black Messiah' to Premiere at Sundance Film Festival|magazine=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Rebecca|last=Rubin|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112180124/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/judas-and-the-black-messiah-sundance-film-festival-1234883365/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片定於2021年2月12日在美國由[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]發行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/judas-and-the-black-messiah-sets-release-for-2021-awards-season-1234660883/|title='Judas And The Black Messiah' Sets Release For 2021 Awards Season|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2020-12-22|access-date=2020-12-22|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223013430/https://deadline.com/2020/12/judas-and-the-black-messiah-sets-release-for-2021-awards-season-1234660883/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國原定於2020年8月21日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/matrix-sequel-release-date-the-flash-akira-off-slate-fred-hampton-movies-warner-bros-1202806896/|title=Warner Bros Sets Release Dates For 'The Matrix' Sequel, 'The Flash' & More; 'Akira' Off Schedule|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|date=2019-12-11|access-date=2019-12-28|archive-date=2019-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218191427/https://deadline.com/2019/12/matrix-sequel-release-date-the-flash-akira-off-slate-fred-hampton-movies-warner-bros-1202806896/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但由於[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情影響而延遲至2021年<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-batman-sopranos-prequel-tom-elvis-presley-movie-warner-bros-release-dates-changes-coronavirus-1202912605/ |title='The Batman' Flies To Fall 2021, 'Sopranos' Prequel Moves To March & More As Warner Bros. Makes Release Date Changes Due To COVID-19 Climate |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2020-04-20 |access-date=2020-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420202338/https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-batman-sopranos-prequel-tom-elvis-presley-movie-warner-bros-release-dates-changes-coronavirus-1202912605/ |archive-date=2020-04-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=CorderoAugust2020>{{Cite news |url=https://ew.com/movies/judas-and-the-black-messiah-trailer-daniel-kaluuya-fred-hampton/ |title=See Daniel Kaluuya as Black Panther leader Fred Hampton in ''Judas and the Black Messiah'' trailer |last=Cordero |first=Rosy |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2020-08-06 |access-date=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807053924/https://ew.com/movies/judas-and-the-black-messiah-trailer-daniel-kaluuya-fred-hampton/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。華納兄弟將該片隨其他旗下電影共同在[[HBO_Max|HBO Max]]上與院線同步上線，為期一個月，並在正常的家用媒體發售前下架。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2020/film/news/warner-bros-hbo-max-theaters-dune-matrix-4-1234845342/ | title = Warner Bros. to Debut Entire 2021 Film Slate, Including 'Dune' and 'Matrix 4,' Both on HBO Max and In Theaters | first = Rebecca | last = Rubin | first2 = Matt | last2 = Donnelly | date = 2020-12-03 | access-date = 2020-12-03 | work = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archive-date = 2020-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201203183130/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/warner-bros-hbo-max-theaters-dune-matrix-4-1234845342/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 反響 ==
評論匯總媒體[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據213篇影評，該片持有96%的新鮮度，平均評分為8.3／10；該網站共識：「《猶大與黑色彌賽亞》對歷史事件進行了令人興奮的劇情改編，是對種族不公的有力譴責，也是其導演和明星的一次重大勝利。」<ref>{{cite web |title= Judas and the Black Messiah (2021) |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/judas_and_the_black_messiah |website= [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher= [[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]] |access-date= 2021-02-06 |archive-date= 2021-01-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210123010848/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/judas_and_the_black_messiah |dead-url= no }}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站根據44位評論家，該片從滿分100分中獲得87分，代表「普遍讚譽」<ref>{{cite web |title= Judas and the Black Messiah Reviews |url= https://www.metacritic.com/movie/judas-and-the-black-messiah |website= [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher= [[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |access-date= 2021-02-05 |archive-date= 2021-02-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210202132629/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/judas-and-the-black-messiah |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的彼得·德布魯（{{lang|en|Peter Debruge}}）撰文稱讚史坦費爾德的表演，並表示：「這部有力的電影將當下時機帶入了嶄新的歷史背景，並暗示矛盾可能是其自身的背叛所形成。」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Debruge|first=Peter|date=2021-02-01|title=‘Judas and the Black Messiah’ Review: Lakeith Stanfield Plays a Rat Among the Panthers|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/reviews/judas-and-the-black-messiah-review-1234894636/|access-date=2021-02-01|work=Variety|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202132612/https://variety.com/2021/film/reviews/judas-and-the-black-messiah-review-1234894636/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》的大衛·魯尼（{{lang|en|David Rooney}}）在評論中寫道：「由丹尼爾·卡盧亞飾演漢普頓和凱斯·史坦費爾德飾演滲透其中的聯邦調查局線人威廉·歐尼爾引起轟動的演出，這是對壓迫與革命、脅迫與背叛的辛辣描述，未受到該主題的普遍而削弱而更加令人震驚。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Rooney|first=David|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/judas-and-the-black-messiah-film-review-sundance-2021|title='Judas and the Black Messiah': Film Review - Sundance 2021|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2021-02-01|access-date=2021-02-01|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202132630/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/judas-and-the-black-messiah-film-review-sundance-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]網站的皮特·哈蒙（{{lang|en|Pete Hammond}}）及《{{le|板巖 (雜誌)|Slate (magazine)|板巖}}》的凱倫·漢（{{lang|en|Karen Han}}）都將片中的各種主題與《[[芝加哥七人案：驚世審判|芝加哥七人案：驚世審判]]》（2020年）的主題作比較，哈蒙認為：「金巧妙地布置了這個未經加工且設定於1968年令人興奮的記述方程式。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/video/judas-and-the-black-messiah-daniel-kaluuya-lakeith-stanfield-sundance/|title=Sundance Review: Daniel Kaluuya And Lakeith Stanfield In ‘Judas And The Black Messiah’|date=2021-02-01|first=Pete|last=Hammond|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202132429/https://deadline.com/video/judas-and-the-black-messiah-daniel-kaluuya-lakeith-stanfield-sundance/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://slate.com/culture/2021/02/judas-black-messiah-movie-review-trial-chicago-7.html|title=Judas and the Black Messiah Offers a Powerful Corrective to The Trial of the Chicago 7|date=2021-02-01|author=Karen Han|website=Slate|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202132415/https://slate.com/culture/2021/02/judas-black-messiah-movie-review-trial-chicago-7.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

